= Unavailable desc = timed out waiting for server handshake\"\",\"\"http.req.id\"\":\"\"6dd66473-6cfe-4102-a6a0-4b5b61028768\"\",\"\"http.req.method\"\":\"\"POST\"\",\"\"http.req.path\"\":\"\"/cart/checkout\"\",\"\"message\"\":\"\"request error\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"8b07fac2-2ba7-4aea-9046-526619a7a8e1\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"error\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-07T14:12:46.58881673Z\"\"}\",出现次数:1\r\naiops-k8s-07,frontend,frontend-1,\"{\"\"error\"\":\"\"failed to complete the order: rpc error: code = Internal desc = shipping quote failure: failed to get shipping quote: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection error: desc = \\\"\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.27.213:50051: i/o timeout\\\"\"\"\",\"\"http.req.id\"\":\"\"9f418b0d-25e7-47e3-8d9d-11c7da507eb5\"\",\"\"http.req.method\"\":\"\"POST\"\",\"\"http.req.path\"\":\"\"/cart/checkout\"\",\"\"message\"\":\"\"request error\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"de050461-585a-4643-bacf-54f01b7b0973\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"error\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-07T14:28:15.73798582Z\"\"}\",出现次数:1\r\naiops-k8s-07,frontend,frontend-1,\"{\"\"error\"\":\"\"failed to complete the order: rpc error: code = Internal desc = shipping quote failure: failed to get shipping quote: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection error: desc = \\\"\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.27.213:50051: i/o timeout\\\"\"\"\",\"\"http.req.id\"\":\"\"b90704d8-efa5-49d8-ab55-328380827023\"\",\"\"http.req.method\"\":\"\"POST\"\",\"\"http.req.path\"\":\"\"/cart/checkout\"\",\"\"message\"\":\"\"request error\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"6253541c-5c57-4e4a-9d22-9acbc92bbeed\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"error\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-07T14:33:28.42157083Z\"\"}\",出现次数:1\r\n", "unique_entities": {"pod_name": ["frontend-0", "frontend-2", "frontend-1"], "service_name": ["frontend"], "node_name": ["aiops-k8s-03", "aiops-k8s-04", "aiops-k8s-07"]}, "matched_anomaly": "Please analyze the abnormal event between 2025-06-07T14:11:03Z and 2025-06-07T14:34:03Z and provide the root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-07 14:11:03+00:00 to 2025-06-07 14:34:03+00:00"}, "log_data_collected": true, "trace_analysis_findings": "```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"latency_spike\",\n    \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\",\n    \"connection_refused\",\n    \"deadline_exceeded\",\n    \"timeout\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"显著延迟 (latency_spike) 出现在 checkoutservice 调用链中，正常时长 9347.60ms 而异常时长延长至 21,668,130.29ms。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"【checkoutservice】调用 【shippingservice】 中的 hipstershop.ShippingService/GetQuote 出现了 connection error 和 i/o timeout，导致请求超时，频次高达 41 次，是主要延迟和错误源。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Frontend 中多处调用返回了 HTTP 500 错误状态码，可能是由于下游调用失败传导。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Frontend 调用 【CheckoutService/PlaceOrder】 返回 HTTP 500 错误，频次 35 次，可能是由于 checkoutservice 的异常传导造成。\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "metric_analysis_findings": "根据分析得到的数据，我发现了一些显著的异常调用链和指标。以下是我的发现：\n\n### Detected Metric Keys\n- error_ratio\n- rrt_max\n- client_error_ratio\n\n### Hypotheses\n\n1. **Component:** cartservice-0\n   - **Reason:** 增加的 `error_ratio` 和 `client_error_ratio` 指标以及延迟升高反映了服务性能问题。\n   - **Evidence:** `error_ratio` 和 `client_error_ratio` 在故障期间显著变化，`normal_p99` 与 `fault_p99` 的变化率达到了100%以上。\n\n2. **Component:** frontend\n   - **Reason:** `rrt_max` 显著升高，推测是由于底层服务或数据库延迟导致的服务性能瓶颈。\n   - **Evidence:** `frontend-0` 和 `frontend-1` 的 `rrt_max` 指标变化率接近2倍，表明响应时间异常增加。\n\n3. **Component:** shippingservice-0\n   - **Reason:** `client_error_ratio` 指标的显著增加表明服务请求失败或超时问题。\n   - **Evidence:** 在故障期间，`client_error_ratio` 和 `error_ratio` 的 `median_change_ratio` 提示服务调用失败率增多。\n\n### 综合判断\n从数据中可以看到多项服务性能指标异常，特别是以 `cartservice` 和 `shippingservice` 表现异常为主。虽然没有直接找到 Node 故障，但需进一步检查底层系统健康状态是否导致这些服务异常。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"error_ratio\", \"rrt_max\", \"client_error_ratio\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Increased error_ratio and client_error_ratio indicators suggest service performance issues.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Significant variations in error_ratio and client_error_ratio between normal and fault p99 values.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Increased rrt_max indicates possible service performance bottleneck due to underlying service or database delays.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Near doubling of rrt_max change ratios in frontend-0 and frontend-1 indicate anomalous response times.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant increase in client_error_ratio suggests service request failures or timeout issues.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Median_change_ratio of client_error_ratio and error_ratio during fault period indicate increased service call failure rates.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n建议进一步调查底层系统异常或资源瓶颈的可能原因。", "log_analysis_findings": "根据提供的日志分析，此事件中最常见的异常模式是与连接超时和服务器握手超时相关的问题。以下是我的分析结果：\n\n### 识别的错误模式\n- 错误类型：`rpc error: code = Unavailable`, `timed out waiting for server handshake`, `i/o timeout`, `transport: Error while dialing`\n- 散布在日志中的关键描述词：`shipping error`, `shipment failed`, `shipping quote failure`, `connection error`\n- 调用链中的错误通常出现在frontend服务与shipping服务之间的交互中。\n\n### 异常分析\n在这些日志中，`frontend` 服务在调用可能涉及 `shipping` 服务操作时，多次展示出 `rpc error` 和 `connection error` 的现象。这种情况表明 `frontend` 服务在尝试与 `shipping` 服务建立连接或执行动作时遇到了网络或服务器响应问题。\n\n### 猜测根因\n1. **网络连接问题**：很可能是 `frontend` 服务所在的环境与 `shipping` 服务之间出现网络连接不稳定或配置问题，导致连接超时。\n2. **`shipping` 服务的可用性**：`shipping` 服务可能由于某种原因在请求的时候未能及时响应，导致超时。\n3. **这种服务故障可能与 DNS 解析错误或者端口配置错误有关**。\n\n### JSON 输出\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\n    \"rpc error: code = Unavailable\",\n    \"timed out waiting for server handshake\",\n    \"i/o timeout\",\n    \"transport: Error while dialing\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Repeated network connection issues or shipping service unavailability during RPC call, causing timeouts\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Shipping error and connection error indicating 'timed out waiting for server handshake' and 'i/o timeout'\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n该故障模式强调了微服务架构中常见的网络连接和服务响应问题，需要检查服务之间的网络配置、DNS设置以及节点状态。"}
